{"word":"πόλεμος","slug":"πόλεμος","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>πόλεμος, ου, ὁ</el></b> [<a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ cp.\">cp.</a> <el>πελεμίζω</el> ‘shock, affect deeply’] ‘armed conflict’<b><p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> in general as state of hostilities <b>war <a href='B:470 24:6'>Mt 24:6</a>; <a href='B:480 13:7'>Mk 13:7</a>; <a href='B:490 14:31'>Lk 14:31</a>; <a href='B:490 21:9'>21:9</a>; <a href='B:650 11:34'>Hb 11:34</a>; <a href='B:730 11:7'>Rv 11:7</a>; <a href='B:730 12:17'>12:17</a>; <a href='B:730 13:7'>13:7</a>; <a href='B:730 19:19'>19:19</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> a hostile encounter as part of a war <b>fight, battle <a href='B:530 14:8'>1 Cor 14:8</a>; <a href='B:730 9:7'>Rv 9:7</a>, <a href='B:730 9:9'>9</a>; <a href='B:730 12:7'>12:7</a>; <a href='B:730 16:14'>16:14</a>; <a href='B:730 20:8'>20:8</a>;</b> hyperbolically <b><a href='B:660 4:1'>Js 4:1</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:πολεμέω\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:πόλις\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}